description:
My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 22

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

Two teams will battle for survival in a sudden death cook-off with guest judges Colin Fassnidge, Guy Grossi, Karen Martini and Liz Egan. In a new twist, all guest judges will be blind tasting the meals for the first time in the competition.
